<section class="kz-sec kz-sec-light"><div class="ctr">
  <h2 class="kz-h2">Order pick and pack Ukraine — structural cost arbitrage with no quality compromise</h2>
  <p>International e-commerce brands evaluating fulfillment options face a binary perception: cheap providers compromise quality, premium providers compromise margins. Ukraine 3PL breaks this binary because the cost advantage comes from structural factors — warehouse rent, picker labor, bundled pricing — not quality cuts. MTP delivers 99.5% pick accuracy (industry standard) at $0.41 per order (60-75% below US/EU baselines).</p>
  <p>Pick and pack accuracy is a system property, not luck. Four independent verification layers — address storage in WMS, pick-stage barcode scan, pack-stage barcode scan, QC checkpoint for high-value — produce measured 99.72% accuracy without depending on individual packer vigilance. If one layer misses an error, the next catches it. This is the same architecture used by premium US/EU 3PL providers; the cost difference comes from where the warehouse is located and what the pickers earn, not from skipped quality steps.</p>
  <p>War-resilience is a structural differentiator that Western 3PL cannot offer because they have never been tested. MTP has shipped 60,000 orders monthly since February 2022 with zero days of fulfillment downtime. Backup power generators, Starlink redundant internet, on-site fuel reserves keep both warehouse facilities (Shchaslyve 2,700 m² and Bilohorodka 1,000 m²) operational through grid disruptions. International carriers (Nova Poshta International, Meest, DHL) continue scheduled pickups. Brands using Ukrainian 3PL during wartime have proven operational continuity that US/EU competitors can only assume.</p>
  <p>MTP fits brands shipping 30-6,000 orders daily with 50-10,000 SKU catalogs. Onboarding takes 3-5 business days. Integrations are native for Shopify, WooCommerce, Etsy, Amazon Seller Central, BigCommerce, Magento, with REST API for custom platforms. Pricing is bundled per-order without stacked fees, peak surcharges, or SKU change penalties. Get pricing for your specific catalog and volume — the form above returns a tailored quote in 15 minutes during business hours.</p>
  <p>See also: <a href="/en/services/">full services portfolio</a>, <a href="/en/calculator/">pricing calculator</a>, <a href="/en/3pl/">3PL logistics overview</a>, <a href="/en/fulfilment-for-books-and-publishers/">book fulfillment Ukraine</a>, <a href="/en/about/">about MTP</a>.</p>
</div></section>

